  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Rigor Declaration">
      Output: 🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL · 📋 REASON: code-impl in BFF (.cs file modification, tag bff-api, ADR-010+013+029 applicable, prompt-handling code is semantically load-bearing) — quality gates Step 9.5 required · Proceeding with Step 0...
