      - Call PromptSchemaOverrideMerger with node.ConfigJson overrides
      - Resolve template variables ({{var}}) from context.PreviousOutputs using the existing helper (mirror AiAnalysisNodeExecutor)
      - Store merged (SystemPrompt, OutputSchema, Temperature) in local variables for the task-004 LLM call
      - Leave a TODO: "LLM call wired in task 004 — see plan.md Wave 1"
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Add structured logging">
      Log at Debug level: node ID, Action ID, merged-prompt length, merged-schema field count. Do NOT log prompt contents (PII / cost).
    </step>
    <step order="6" name="Build">
      Run: dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/ — expect 0 errors, 0 new warnings.
